OL,3,CChristmas getaway expected to be the
OL,4,Cbusiest on record
OL,6,FThis year's Christmas getaway is
OL,7,Fexpected to be the busiest on record,
OL,8,Fnew figures suggest.
OL,10,FThe AA forecast that traffic for all
OL,11,Fjourneys in the run-up to December 25
OL,12,Fwill peak on Friday when about 24.4
OL,13,Fmillion cars are expected on the UK's
OL,14,Froads.
OL,16,FA total of 37.5 million leisure trips
OL,17,Fby car are planned between Wednesday
OL,18,Fand Christmas Eve, the RAC estimated.
OL,19,FThat is the most in the week before
OL,20,FChristmas Day since the company began
OL,21,Frecording the data in 2013.
