OL,3,CChristmas getaway expected to be the
OL,4,Cbusiest on record
OL,6,FOn Saturday and Christmas Eve, drivers
OL,7,Fare being warned the worst hold-ups
OL,8,Fwill be between 11am and 7pm. Although
OL,9,FChristmas Eve is anticipated to see a
OL,10,Fslight drop in journeys to 22.7
OL,11,Fmillion, with an estimated 18.3
OL,12,Fmillion cars on the road on Christmas
OL,13,FDay.
OL,15,FAdding to the challenge will be the
OL,16,Fclosure of the M27 motorway in both
OL,17,Fdirections between Junctions 9 and 11
OL,18,Ffrom 8pm on Christmas Eve until 4am on
OL,19,FJanuary 4 for major works, affecting
OL,20,Fjourneys between Southampton and
OL,21,FPortsmouth.
