OL,3,CChristmas getaway expected to be the
OL,4,Cbusiest on record
OL,6,FDrivers warned over severe delays as
OL,7,Fstretch of M27 to close both ways for
OL,8,F12 days over Christmas
OL,10,FAnd the Port of Dover estimates nearly
OL,11,F30,000 cars will embark on outbound
OL,12,Fsailings during the festive period,
OL,13,Fwith traffic peaking between 6am and
OL,14,F1pm from Friday to Sunday.
OL,16,FShaun Jones, AA expert patrol, said:
OL,17,F"It's beginning to look a lot like
OL,18,Ftraffic. Our advice is simple: plan
OL,19,Fahead, check your route and allow
OL,20,Fextra time. Patience will be your best
OL,21,Fpresent this year."
