OL,3,CChristmas getaway expected to be the
OL,4,Cbusiest on record
OL,6,FRAC mobile servicing and repairs team
OL,7,Fleader Nick Mullender said: "With
OL,8,Frecord numbers predicted to be taking
OL,9,Fto the roads this Christmas, journeys
OL,10,Fhave the potential to be Grinch-worthy
OL,11,Fwithout some careful planning. The
OL,12,Fweek before Christmas is one of the
OL,13,Ffew times of year when most of the UK
OL,14,Fhits the road simultaneously, with
OL,15,F2025 looking to be the busiest getaway
OL,16,Fperiod since our records began."
