OL,3,CChristmas getaway expected to be the
OL,4,Cbusiest on record
OL,6,FNational Highways, which manages
OL,7,FEngland's motorways and major A roads,
OL,8,Fsaid it will "remove as many roadworks
OL,9,Fas we safely can so everyone can get
OL,10,Fwhere they need to go this Christmas".
OL,12,FMeanwhile engineering work by Network
OL,13,FRail will lead to more pressure on the
OL,14,Froads, with several of the UK's
OL,15,Fbusiest railway lines disrupted.
OL,16,FLondon Waterloo, one of the UK's
OL,17,Fbusiest stations, will be closed to
OL,18,Ftrains between Christmas Day and
OL,19,FDecember 28, and will have a reduced
OL,20,Ftimetable between December 29 and
OL,21,FJanuary 4.
