OL,3,CChristmas getaway expected to be the
OL,4,Cbusiest on record
OL,6,FAnd for those jetting off to other
OL,7,Fcountries the UK airports are also
OL,8,Fexpecting their busiest Christmas
OL,9,Fgetaway in history.
OL,11,FThe Civil Aviation Authority said
OL,12,Fpassenger numbers for December are
OL,13,Fforecast to exceed the record 22
OL,14,Fmillion seen last year. Heathrow, the
OL,15,FUK's busiest airport, is preparing for
OL,16,Fmore than 7 million passengers to
OL,17,Ftravel through its four terminals this
OL,18,Fmonth.
